0.05
  - Add POD documentation.
  - Add 'Contributors && Kudos' section to documentation.
  - Simplify dependencies blocks.
  - Prevent 'build' dependencies to be installed for end-users.

0.04
  - Prepare distribution to be released to CPAN.

0.03
  - ListBlobs: For convenience, enable auto-retrieval of paginated results. When the call parameter 'auto_retrieve_paginated_results' is set to 1, the client will automatically perform additional requests under the hood and return the complete list of blobs.

0.02
  - Add 'DeleteBlob' API call.
  - Remove warning on Signer service, related to the concatenation of an uninitialized string (empty headers).

0.01
  - Initial release.
